Class DeclareNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.java.latexee.declareast.DeclareNode
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MacroDeclaration, OperatorDeclaration

    public abstract class DeclareNode
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract class for MacroDeclaration and OperatorDeclaration. Describes fields and methods which are common for MacroDeclaration and OperatorDeclaration, such as content dictionary, meaning, misc. information contained and ID
